Page should auto detect user closest server and display it

Precondition:
- User has to be in main page
- User is not using a VPN

Steps:
- Click on "start"

Expected result:
- The server should be displayed to the user, and should recieve input of their download and upload speed based on the closest server automaticly, unleast modified before hand

Enviorment:
- Chrome 120
- Windows 10

Source: https://www.speedtest.net/
